#CircuitBreakerSG D-27
Waking up to some big breakfast or rather brunch on a no-alarm Sunday.

Having grilled thick toast sandwich with cheese & @AyamBrandSG Spicy Tuna. Serve with crispy hash browns, greens & strawberries. Fuel up with some Nespresso compatible Coffee from @LorEspressoSG.

Happy Sunday!

Your breakfasts are just as good as the dinners 🤤

I want this big breakfast Yvonne!! 😋😋
@in_frans_kitchen Too lazy to wake up esp on weekends 😆
Oh wow...this is breakfast definitely worth waking up especially early for! 😋😍❤️
Say wow to the toast and the hashbrowns 😋❤️
How's the capsule compared to nespresso?
Yummy. The Color n the food looks good 😍
Wow yummy!! May I know how to make the filling for the sandwich? Thanks!

Thank you for pledging to #StayHomeWithAscott. #CapitaLandHopeFoundation will be making a donation of US$10 to Save The Children and we look forward to more of your #StayHomeWithAscott posts. Stay home, stay safe and cook away!
